no-process-env.description:
Description

This rule is aimed at discouraging use ofprocess.envto avoid global dependencies. As such, it will warn wheneverprocess.envis used.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-process-env: "error"*/

if(process.env.NODE_ENV === "development") {
    //...
}

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-process-env: "error"*/

var config = require("./config");

if(config.env === "development") {
    //...
}
